<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Deal Approval Required</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35 0%, #f7931e 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .alert-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .alert-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3e0 0%, #ffe0b2 100%);
            border: 2px solid #ff6b35;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .alert-box::before {
            content: "üîî";
            position: absolute;
            top: -15px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: #ff6b35;
            color: white;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .deal-preview {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .deal-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        
        .deal-icon {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-right: 15px;
            color: #ff6b35;
        }
        
        .deal-title {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .deal-details {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            padding: 15px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff6b35;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #ff6b35;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .description-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
        }
        
        .description-box h4 {
            color: #28a745;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .description-box p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .merchant-info {
            background: #e8f5e8;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
        }
        
        .merchant-info h4 {
            color: #28a745;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .merchant-details {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .merchant-detail {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 200px;
        }
        
        .merchant-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #28a745;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .merchant-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        .action-required {
            background: #ffebee;
            border: 2px solid #f44336;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .action-required h4 {
            color: #d32f2f;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .action-required p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button.approve {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .cta-button.reject {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #c82333 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .cta-button.review {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35 0%, #f7931e 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .stats-summary {
            background: #f0f8f0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
        }
        
        .stats-summary h4 {
            color: #28a745;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(120px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #28a745;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .deal-details {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .merchant-details {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .merchant-detail {
                min-width: auto;
            }
            
            .cta-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            
            .cta-button {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 250px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="alert-icon">üéØ</div>
            <h1>New Deal Approval Required</h1>
            <p>Merchant Deal Submission</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                Hi {{adminName}},
            </p>
            
            <div class="alert-box">
                <h2 style="color: #ff6b35; margin-bottom: 15px;">New Deal Pending Approval</h2>
                <p style="color: #666; font-size: 16px;">
                    A merchant has submitted a new deal that requires your review and approval before it goes live.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="deal-preview">
                <div class="deal-header">
                    <div class="deal-icon">üè∑Ô∏è</div>
                    <h3 class="deal-title">{{dealTitle}}</h3>
                </div>
                
                <div class="deal-details">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Category</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{dealCategory}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Discount</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{discount}}{{#if (eq discountType 'percentage')}}%{{else if (eq discountType 'fixed')}} GHS{{/if}} OFF</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Original Price</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{#if originalPrice}}GHS {{originalPrice}}{{else}}Not specified{{/if}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Discounted Price</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{#if discountedPrice}}GHS {{discountedPrice}}{{else}}Not specified{{/if}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Valid Until</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{validUntil}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Submission Date</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{submissionDate}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="description-box">
                    <h4>üìù Deal Description</h4>
                    <p>{{dealDescription}}</p>
                </div>
                
                {{#if termsConditions}}
                <div class="description-box">
                    <h4>üìã Terms & Conditions</h4>
                    <p>{{termsConditions}}</p>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="merchant-info">
                <h4>üè™ Merchant Information</h4>
                <div class="merchant-details">
                    <div class="merchant-detail">
                        <div class="merchant-label">Business Name</div>
                        <div class="merchant-value">{{businessName}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="merchant-detail">
                        <div class="merchant-label">Contact Email</div>
                        <div class="merchant-value">{{merchantEmail}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="action-required">
                <h4>‚ö° Action Required</h4>
                <p>
                    Please review this deal submission and decide whether to approve or reject it. 
                    The merchant is waiting for your decision to make their deal available to customers.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-buttons">
                <a href="{{reviewUrl}}" class="cta-button review">Review Deal</a>
                <a href="{{approveUrl}}" class="cta-button approve">Quick Approve</a>
                <a href="{{rejectUrl}}" class="cta-button reject">Reject Deal</a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: #e3f2fd; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0; text-align: center;">
                <h4 style="color: #1976d2; margin-bottom: 15px;">‚è∞ Review Guidelines</h4>
                <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    Please review and respond within <strong>24-48 hours</strong> to maintain good merchant experience.
                </p>
                <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
                    Quick responses help keep merchants engaged and encourage more quality deal submissions.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Indians in Ghana - Admin Dashboard</strong></p>
            <p>You're receiving this notification because you're an admin.</p>
            <p>üìß Admin Support: admin@indiansinghana.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
